For more information e-mail This home includes the finest in luxury, including an indoor pool and hot tub; personal gym; private outdoor tennis court; wine room; theater room; private office; formal dining for 12; elevator; air conditioning and radiant heat; Wi-Fi internet; and only 3.2 miles to town! This elegant estate is situated on a private 2.26-acre lot in the gated community of Starwood, with big, spectacular views and just minutes to downtown Aspen. This home is 13,500 square feet and can accommodate 16+ people. The ultimate in luxury! Private Homes Condo Complex:
